'''
Given an array A of size N of integers. Your task is to find the minimum, maximum and sum of the elements in the array.
'''

You don't need to read input or print anything. 
Your task is to complete the function getMinMax() which takes the array A[] and its size N as inputs and returns the minimum and maximum element of the array.

def getMinMax( a, n):
    return (min(a),max(a),sum(a))
